## Core Concepts (Anyone Can Understand)  

### 1. Username Guessing (Task 2)  
**The Trick:** Websites tell you if username exists  
Try "admin" â†’ "Wrong password" = ADMIN EXISTS! ğŸ¯
Try "xyz123" â†’ "No user found" = DOESN'T EXIST âŒ


**Why it works:** Lazy error messages give away valid usernames  

### 2. Password Guessing (Task 3)  
**The Method:** Computer tries 1000s passwords fast  
Tool: Hydra (like super-fast typing robot)
Passwords: admin, 123456, password123, rockyou.txt list

**Smart way:** Go slow to avoid lockout  

### 3. Broken Login Logic (Task 4)  
**The Bug:** Website doesn't check properly  
Normal: username=admin&password=secret123
Broken: username=admin&password= (EMPTY!) â†’ LOGS IN! ğŸ˜±

**Common mistakes:** 
- Empty password works
- Clicks "Login" button = auto login  
- Forgets to check password field  

### 4. Cookie Tricks (Task 5)  
**What are cookies?** Tiny notes browser keeps  
Normal cookie: user=john; admin=false
Hacked cookie: user=john; admin=true â†’ ADMIN ACCESS! ğŸ†


**How:** Browser extension changes cookie value

